<!--<h4>First Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī prittivipati rājulladēvuḷ cari <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> lla <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ṇḍapa <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> llakrāmunṟu pritivipatūlla 
<lb n="2"/>Iccinna pannaśā karu veṁggaḷanṟu cāmuḷakku mōrayaku muppadi maṟūtūru raccamanampuna 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>kulocinaṭṭi podopuḷu racca kālu Ūrupen kālu puṟṟa nūrullu mācūrullu koṇḍapaṟu 
<lb n="4"/>dēniṭiccūvānṟu pañcamahapātaka sañuttunṟugun 
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="5"/>tēni rakṣiñci kuḍipinavānṟu 
<lb n="6"/>Aḍugu Aḍugu Asvamēdaṁmpuna pallampukāñcun 
</p>

<!--<h4>Third Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="7"/>vallavaru <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="8"/>tēnikkina <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="9"/>[E]ccu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
</p>

